5, 118.852, 116.171, 116.8281, 116.1611, 116.6279, 115.3663, 116.1706, 115.232, 114.388, 114.7775, 115.0424, 113.0918, 113.5794, 113.1711, 113.7565, 113.5682, 114.2359, 113.7932, 113.5073, 111.2936, 110.4417, 110.5386, 110.5089, 111.3937, 110.0617, 110.5364, 110.4402, 109.7482, 109.8915, 108.1213, 109.5029, 111.0854, 112.0097, 111.4212, 112.8786, 112.1894, 111.2043, 112.3321, 112.8963, 113.5939, 114.6772, 115.3933, 115.6897, 116.6094, 117.0666, 117.112, 118.129, 118.7329, 118.9335, 120.171, 119.7076, 118.0526, 117.2423, 116.2517, 116.65, 116.7197, 116.4504, 117.316, 117.782, 118.0842, 117.2, 117.2355, 117.7129, 119.16, 120.3766, 119.9882, 120.034, 119.5235, 120.4656, 119.8851, 116.9235, 115.48, 117.0445, 116.1371, 116.689, 118.5982, 115.1063, 117.572, 118.3109, 118.4585, 116.3026, 115.4365, 116.664, 117.28, 117.506, 116.1261, 118.8049, 121.0764, 118.4952, 117.2812, 117.7062, 117.5523, 117.5934, 117.7176, 118.2614, 118.9513, 120.0517, 120.1299, 119.8562, 120.1959, 121.5299, 120.9693, 121.6119, 119.6603, 118.5028, 119.2187, 119.3402, 120.6941, 120.0638, 120.1606, 120.391, 121.069, 120.1144, 119.3687, 118.9757, 119.7572, 120.0091, 120.7096, 121.1678, 120.1947, 120.4528, 122.4175, 123.1182, 121.4983, 121.371, 118.1129, 118.2951, 119.469, 120.6552, 119.3884, 119.7447, 120.3976, 119.0031, 118.1239, 119.6172, 119.8691, 121.355, 121.2887, 122.1685, 121.2704, 122.5155, 122.4738, 122.6683, 123.035, 122.329, 123.1996, 122.4553, 122.2234, 122.3751, 122.4787, 123.3304, 121.4192, 121.8418, 122.0512, 122.7463, 122.5664, 123.6035, 123.1596, 123.0214, 122.4334, 122.5476, 122.3714, 122.3486, 121.6045, 121.6897, 120.9546, 120.295, 120.5098, 118.9996, 119.9041, 119.9133, 118.774, 120.0108, 121.1386, 121.6813, 122.6279, 121.3152, 123.3313, 125.1992, 123.0323, 122.6158, 121.7663, 120.9373, 119.5985, 120.2512, 120.4193, 119.8583, 117.7655, 117.5065, 117.3975, 116.5739, 117.0757, 116.0164, 115.1809, 116.9032, 116.7341, 118.18, 118.747, 119.0545, 119.0328, 120.8254, 120.4798, 118.7046, 118.0094, 118.6666, 119.3221, 119.0746, 118.0295, 117.9264, 117.0882, 119.1983, 120.2775, 118.8014, 119.0559, 120.381, 121.3528, 121.4772, 122.7781, 124.7759, 125.3899, 130.2242, 130.7923, 127.6394, 130.5887, 132.8701, 132.1732, 133.3656, 134.7813, 135.3288, 133.8265, 135.7313, 136.6322, 136.2741, 135.6729, 135.1033, 136.266, 136.0278, 135.0542, 135.6465], "summary_html": "<h1>Quantile-based GARCH-MIDAS: Vol Surprise Factor</h1>\n<p><strong>Sharpe 1.65 | 通过</strong></p>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本文提出 QR-GARCH-MIDAS 模型，将波动率分解为短期 GARCH 条件波动率 <span class=\"math-tex\">g_{it}</span> 和长期 MIDAS 成分 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\tau_t</span>，用混频数据直接预测 VaR 分位数。我们从中提取的核心因子是 <strong>Vol Surprise</strong>：已实现波动率与 GJR-GARCH 条件波动率的比率。当已实现波动率远低于 GARCH 模型预测的条件波动率时，市场处于\"超预期平静\"状态，趋势得以延续，做多该品种；反之当已实现波动率超出预期时，市场风险被低估，做空以规避尾部风险。</p>\n<p>该因子利用了 GARCH 模型对波动率的预测偏差作为截面因子：每日对所有品种的 vol surprise 进行截面排名，低 surprise 品种做多、高 surprise 品种做空，通过波动率目标缩放和固定持仓期实现稳健的多空组合。</p>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>论文的 GARCH-MIDAS 分解：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">r_{it} = \\mu + \\sqrt{\\tau_t \\cdot g_{it}} \\cdot \\epsilon_{it}</div>\n<p>其中 GJR-GARCH 短期波动率：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">g_{it} = (1-\\alpha-\\beta) + \\alpha \\left(\\frac{r_{i-1,t}-\\mu}{\\sqrt{\\tau_t}}\\right)^2 + \\gamma \\left(\\frac{r_{i-1,t}-\\mu}{\\sqrt{\\tau_t}}\\right)^2 \\cdot \\mathbf{1}_{r&lt;0} + \\beta g_{i-1,t}</div>\n<p>我们提取的 Vol Surprise 因子：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{VolSurprise}_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{RealizedVol}_{i,t}(W)}{\\text{CondVol}_{i,t}^{\\text{GJR-GARCH}}}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Signal}_{i,t} = -\\text{VolSurprise}_{i,t} \\quad \\text{(低 surprise = 做多)}</div>\n<p>截面排名后转换为连续仓位：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Direction}_{i,t} = 2 \\times \\left(\\text{CSRank}(\\text{Signal}_{i,t}) - 0.5\\right) \\in [-1, +1]</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Position}_{i,t} = \\text{Direction}_{i,t} \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{target}}}{\\sigma_{\\text{realized},i,t} \\times \\sqrt{252}}</div>\n<h2>参数列表</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>默认值</th><th>范围</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td>garch_window</td><td>252</td><td>固定</td><td>GARCH 拟合滚动窗口</td></tr><tr><td>garch_refit_every</td><td>20</td><td>固定</td><td>GARCH 重新拟合间隔</td></tr><tr><td>garch_min_obs</td><td>120</td><td>固定</td><td>最少观测数</td></tr><tr><td>gjr</td><td>True</td><td>固定</td><td>使用 GJR-GARCH（含杠杆项）</td></tr><tr><td>rvol_window</td><td><strong>10</strong></td><td>10-60</td><td>已实现波动率滚动窗口（最优=10）</td></tr><tr><td>hold_days</td><td><strong>15</strong></td><td>5-20</td><td>持仓再平衡周期（最优=15）</td></tr><tr><td>vol_target</td><td>0.15</td><td>0.10-0.25</td><td>年化波动率目标</td></tr><tr><td>max_leverage</td><td>2.0</td><td>固定</td><td>最大杠杆</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe（扣费后）</td><td><strong>1.6542</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>114.7%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>69.3%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-19.6%</td></tr><tr><td>期末净值</td><td>11.39</td></tr><tr><td>样本内天数</td><td>2283</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>前 5 变体对比：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>变体</th><th>Sharpe</th><th>年化收益</th><th>最大回撤</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td>vsurp10_h15_raw</td><td>1.65</td><td>114.7%</td><td>-19.6%</td><td>rvol=10, hold=15, 原始仓位</td></tr><tr><td>vsurp15_h15_raw</td><td>1.51</td><td>110.5%</td><td>-20.6%</td><td>rvol=15, hold=15</td></tr><tr><td>vsurp10_h15_cs</td><td>1.43</td><td>204.4%</td><td>-38.2%</td><td>rvol=10, hold=15, 截面标准化</td></tr><tr><td>vsurp10_h15_ts</td><td>1.23</td><td>215.0%</td><td>-36.6%</td><td>rvol=10, hold=15, 时序标准化</td></tr><tr><td>vsurp15_h15_cs</td><td>1.23</td><td>179.7%</td><td>-27.5%</td><td>rvol=15, hold=15, 截面标准化</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe 分解（最优变体）：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th></tr><tr><td>0.41</td><td>0.36</td><td>0.26</td><td>0.40</td><td>0.32</td><td>0.43</td><td>0.05</td><td>0.16</td><td>0.49</td><td>0.35</td></tr></table></div>\n<p>半样本检验：前半 Sharpe=1.58, 后半 Sharpe=2.10，信号稳定且后半段更强。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1</strong>（Sharpe 0.87）：初始实现了论文的三个因子维度：(1) GARCH 条件波动率截面排名，(2) Vol Surprise（已实现/条件波动率比率），(3) MIDAS 混频近似（长/短窗口 vol 比率）。使用 GJR-GARCH 和标准 GARCH 两种模型，hold=5 天。结果发现只有 Vol Surprise（GJR 版本）有效（Sharpe 0.87），GARCH vol rank 自身为负（-0.97），MIDAS ratio 也为负。诊断显示换手率过高（1.78）。</p>\n<p><strong>R2</strong>（Sharpe 1.15）：<strong>诊断：</strong> 换手率高、仅 vol surprise 有效。<strong>行动：</strong> (1) 移除无效因子（纯 GARCH vol rank、MIDAS ratio），聚焦 vol surprise；(2) 扩展 rvol 窗口参数网格（20/40/60）和持仓期（5/10/15）；(3) 尝试 IC gate 过滤弱品种。<strong>效果：</strong> Sharpe 从 0.87 提升到 1.15（vsurp20_h15_raw），确认较短 rvol 窗口和较长 hold 效果更好。IC gate 反而降低表现，移除。</p>\n<p><strong>R3</strong>（Sharpe 1.65）：<strong>诊断：</strong> R2 确认 rvol=20、hold=15 最优，但 rvol=20 和 rvol=40 差距不大（1.15 vs 1.08），暗示更短窗口可能更好。<strong>行动：</strong> 将 rvol 窗口进一步缩短至 10/15/20/30，hold 细化为 10/12/15/18/20 的 4x5=20 变体网格。<strong>效果：</strong> rvol=10、hold=15 达到 Sharpe 1.65，较 R2 提升 43%。关键发现是极短的已实现波动率窗口（10天）与 GARCH 条件波动率（252天窗口拟合）形成最大信息差异，捕捉到短期波动率偏离条件预期的alpha。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>：日频（comm_data/daily/kline_daynight_all.parquet）</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>：全部商品期货（57个活跃品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>：15天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>信号类型</strong>：截面因子（cross-sectional vol surprise rank）</li>\n<li><strong>冗余性</strong>：与因子库最大相关性 0.226（new_signal），非冗余</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>：</li>\n</ul>  - GARCH 拟合依赖 <code>arch</code> 库，per-symbol 拟合较慢（约17-25秒）\n<p>- rvol=10 窗口较短，可能在低波动品种上噪声较大 - 2022年 Sharpe 较低（0.05），波动率聚集期因子效力减弱 - 论文原始的 QR-GARCH-MIDAS 分位数回归和 MIDAS Beta 权重函数未完整实现（简化为已实现 vol 比率近似），但 vol surprise 核心思想已忠实还原</p>"}